  <name>PDF4QT</name>
  <summary>Advanced PDF viewer and editor with modern glassmorphism UI</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      PDF4QT is a comprehensive PDF viewer and editor featuring a modern glassmorphism user interface
      with translucent, floating toolbars and smooth animations. It provides advanced PDF functionality
      based on PDF Reference 2.0.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Modern glassmorphism UI with floating, draggable toolbars</li>
      <li>Automatic light/dark theme adaptation</li>
      <li>Advanced document viewing and editing capabilities</li>
      <li>Multithreading support for smooth performance</li>
      <li>Encryption and signature validation</li>
      <li>Color management system</li>
      <li>Text layout analysis and text-to-speech</li>
      <li>Form filling and annotation support</li>
      <li>Document comparison and optimization tools</li>
      <li>Audio book conversion</li>
      <li>Command line tools</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
